      <scopecontent id="aspace_848336ef920a53edeee89e58c89f486e">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This collection consists of audio and video material about the Yale Center for British Art that has been created by other entities. Highlights of the collection include media about the opening of the Center, documentaries from television and public radio related to the Center and its exhibitions, and the film "Something to Brighten up the Morning" about Paul Mellon's horse Mill Reef.</p>
      </scopecontent>
